OL,3,CIranian foreign minister in Russia for
OL,4,Ctalks with Putin on US conflict
OL,6,FIranian Foreign Minister Abbas
OL,7,FAraghchi has arrived in Russia for a
OL,8,Fmeeting with President Vladimir Putin,
OL,9,Famid a stalemate in peace discussions
OL,10,Fwith the United States.
OL,12,FThe state-run IRNA news agency said
OL,13,FAraghchi landed in St. Petersburg for
OL,14,Fhis meeting with Putin on Monday.
OL,16,FAraghchi visited Islamabad, Pakistan,
OL,17,Ftwice over the weekend, as well as
OL,18,FMuscat, Oman - which shares the Strait
OL,19,Fof Hormuz with the Islamic Republic -
OL,20,Fas negotiations to end the US and
OL,21,FIsrael's war with Iran appear stalled.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777327868
OL,3,CIranian foreign minister in Russia for
OL,4,Ctalks with Putin on US conflict
OL,6,FHe also spoke by phone with
OL,7,Fcounterparts in Qatar and Saudi Arabia
OL,8,Fon Sunday.
OL,10,FIn a pre-recorded interview posted by
OL,11,FIRNA, Araghchi said: "It is a good
OL,12,Fopportunity for us to consult with our
OL,13,FRussian friends about the developments
OL,14,Fthat have occurred in relation to the
OL,15,Fwar during this period and what is
OL,16,Fhappening now."
OL,18,FAraghchi said it was Washington's
OL,19,Fapproach that "caused the negotiations
OL,20,Fto be delayed" that had been planned
OL,21,Fin Islamabad.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
