OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777327868
OL,3,CIranian foreign minister in Russia for
OL,4,Ctalks with Putin on US conflict
OL,6,F"The previous one, despite the
OL,7,Fprogress that had been made, could not
OL,8,Fachieve its goals," he said, blaming
OL,9,Fwhat he called "excessive demands" by
OL,10,Fhis American counterparts.
OL,12,FTrump has questioned who is in charge
OL,13,Fin Iran at the moment and said
OL,14,Fconfusion within its theocracy made it
OL,15,Fdifficult to reach a deal.
OL,17,FPakistan hopes to revive stalled
OL,18,Fnegotiations
OL,26,@pD@SO]qD@POUqD@bO]
