OL,3,CIranian foreign minister in Russia for
OL,4,Ctalks with Putin on US conflict
OL,6,FOn Saturday, the US president said he
OL,7,Fhad cancelled special envoys Jared
OL,8,FKushner and Steve Witkoff's planned
OL,9,Ftrip to Pakistan, which has been
OL,10,Facting as a mediator.
OL,12,FHe claimed this was because the trip
OL,13,Fwould involve "a lot of travelling",
OL,14,Fconsidering Iran refused to meet
OL,15,Fdirectly with US officials, preferring
OL,16,Fto use Pakistan as a go-between,
OL,17,Fdespite an earlier round of face-to-
OL,18,Fface talks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
