PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777327868
OL,3,CIranian foreign minister in Russia for
OL,4,Ctalks with Putin on US conflict
OL,6,FTwo regional officials, speaking on
OL,7,Fcondition of anonymity, said on Monday
OL,8,Fthat Iran has offered to end its
OL,9,Fchokehold on the Strait of Hormuz, a
OL,10,Fcritical waterway through which a
OL,11,Ffifth of the world's oil passes, in
OL,12,Fexchange for the US lifting a blockade
OL,13,Fof Iran's ports.
OL,15,FTehran is also reported to have
OL,16,Fproposed that discussions about its
OL,17,Fnuclear programme would come in a
OL,18,Flater phase.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
