OL,3,CIranian foreign minister in Russia for
OL,4,Ctalks with Putin on US conflict
OL,6,FThe nuclear issue is one of the US and
OL,7,FIsrael's key reasons to go to war on
OL,8,FFebruary 28, meaning Trump is unlikely
OL,9,Fto accept such an offer.
OL,11,FPakistan has been seeking to revive
OL,12,Fstalled talks between Iran and the US.
OL,14,FCeasefire remains fragile as another
OL,15,F14 people killed in Lebanon
OL,17,FIsraeli strikes in southern Lebanon on
OL,18,FSunday killed 14 people, including two
OL,19,Fchildren, according to health
OL,20,Fofficials, marking the deadliest day
OL,21,Fsince a ceasefire began ten days ago.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
