OL,3,CIranian foreign minister in Russia for
OL,4,Ctalks with Putin on US conflict
OL,6,FIn total, 47 people in Lebanon have
OL,7,Fbeen killed by Israeli fire since the
OL,8,Ftruce came into effect at midnight
OL,9,Flocal time on April 17, according to a
OL,10,Ftally by ITV News' North American
OL,11,Fpartner CNN.
OL,13,FSeven people were killed on Saturday,
OL,14,Faccording to Lebanon's health
OL,15,Fministry, despite the ceasefire, which
OL,16,Fhas been extended by another three
OL,17,Fweeks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
