OL,3,CIranian foreign minister in Russia for
OL,4,Ctalks with Putin on US conflict
OL,6,FIran-backed militant group Hezbollah,
OL,7,Fone of the world's most powerful non-
OL,8,Fstate actors, is not a party to the
OL,9,Fceasefire agreement and has previously
OL,10,Fsaid it would not abide by it.
OL,12,FThe group said it launched five
OL,13,Fattacks on the Israeli military in
OL,14,FLebanon on Sunday, including one that
OL,15,Fkilled an Israeli soldier in the
OL,16,Fsouthern town of Taybeh.
OL,18,FEarlier on Sunday, the Israeli
OL,19,Fmilitary said it had intercepted three
OL,20,Fdrones before they crossed the border.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
