OL,3,CIranian foreign minister in Russia for
OL,4,Ctalks with Putin on US conflict
OL,6,FThe Israel Defence Forces (IDF) told
OL,7,FCNN on Sunday that forces "conducted
OL,8,Fartillery and aerial strikes targeting
OL,9,Fterrorists and military infrastructure
OL,10,Fsites" belonging to Hezbollah.
OL,12,FRights groups say Israel's military
OL,13,Foffensive in Lebanon is mirroring
OL,14,Ftactics used in Gaza - from heavy
OL,15,Fstrikes on critical infrastructure and
OL,16,Fhealthcare facilities, to the
OL,17,Ftargeting of journalists and
OL,18,Fpsychological warfare.
