OL,3,CIranian foreign minister in Russia for
OL,4,Ctalks with Putin on US conflict
OL,6,FThe Israeli military raided the
OL,7,Fnorthern town of Zawtar al-Sharqiya on
OL,8,FSunday, attacking and destroying a
OL,9,Fmosque, Lebanon's National News Agency
OL,10,F(NNA) reported.
OL,12,FAlong a belt of neighbourhoods below
OL,13,Fthe Litani River, the military
OL,14,Ftargeted homes and infrastructure up
OL,15,Fto the town of Yaroun, about 23
OL,16,Fkilometres (14 miles) south, near the
OL,17,Fborder with Israel, NNA added.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
